Posts.Content: Jun 29, 2013 05:28AM DaniellaBella wrote: I'm 27 and was diagnosed at 26. I live in SI but work in NYC. I found a great monthly support group for premenopausal women in NYC. The women were in their 20's through late 30's. It's called Young Survival Coalition f2f network. Google it. So happy I went. I hadn't felt that normal nor had anyone to relate to in a very long time.
